data.title: SoundtrackINFO: The Secret Garden Soundtrack
data.meta_description: The Secret Garden soundtrack, music by composer Zbigniew Preisner
data.text:
1. Main Title [3:33] 2. Leaving The Docks [1:27] 3. Mary Downstairs [2:05] 4. First Time Outside [1:24] 5. Skipping Rope [0:53] ...see complete tracklist Soundtrack Q & A Q: Do you know where I can find the sheet music for the theme from this movie?? (from Shannon in West Chester, PA) A: Try searching for "sheet music" at Google.com and see if you can find it at all the websites that come up in the results. If that doesn't work, search for the composer's homepage and then send an email to the composer's page. (thanks to OSTfan, Burlingame) add more info A: Try sheetmusicplus.com (thanks to VICTORIA, LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA) add more info Q: Does anyone know the name of the song playing at the end? (from Erin in MI) A: "Winter Light" by Linda Ronstadt (thanks to Burryberry, Cardiff) add more info Q: What's the music playing when Lord Craven is sitting in his chair dreaming about the garden? (from stevex in Australia) A: I think it's called "Craven's Return" (thanks to fantasyprincess, Oakland,CA) add more info Q: What's the song the woman is singing when she's rolling the dough? (from Kammy in California) A: "Greensleeves" written by Henry the 8th (thanks to Megan, PA) add more info Q: Where can I get sheet music for the song "Leaving the Docks?" (from Diane Bosworth in Holts Summit, MO) A: Try sheetmusicplus.com (thanks to Travis) add more info Q: What is the march that is heard when she lands the ship in India?

...from pedro2001 in Lima, Peru (answer pedro2001's question) Feedback  Email this page to anyone.  Ask a question about the music in this movie.  Add music info heard in the movie but not listed on the soundtrack CD.  Add other info not listed above (trivial anecdotes, press quotes, recording anomalies, etc).
